headline: Congresswoman With Stake In Musk's xAI Adds Position In Tesla's Robot Rival Apptronik
summary: A congresswoman owns a stake in Elon Musk's xAI and now owns a stake in Apptronik, a company trying to beat Musk's robotic ambitions.
